**Reaper* | Solo Killing - Nightmare Team | Haunted
__Basics__
The Reaper can banish players to steal their powers.
__Details__
Banishing is an end night action.
The Reaper cannot banish on consecutive nights.
When the Reaper banishes a player, it gains their role as its own extra role. If the gained role had abilities with limited uses, the Reaper regains all its uses once obtained.
The Reaper wins when it is the last player alive.
When the Reaper dies it does not become a ghost and is immediately banished.
__Simplified__
The Reaper can banish players to steal their powers. It can do so on non-consecutive nights.
The Reaper wins when it is the last player alive.
__Formalized__
Haunted Role

__Card__
The Reaper can banish players to steal their powers.
